        <num>CCP 612</num>
        <heading>612.  Representation</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 612.  Representation
One or more members of the class, who will fairly ensure the adequate representation of all members, may sue or be sued in a derivative class action on behalf of all members.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=112194</p>
